{"id":"entities/charis","title":"Charis","type":"entities","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>Stub. First mentioned in <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2025-05-09-initiation-to-chelympics-1-beer-1-shot-per-person\">2025 05 09 initiation to chelympics 1 beer 1 shot per person</a>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Friend in <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/yahir-family\">Yahir</a>'s circle. Hosts the <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/chelympics\">Chelympics</a> halftime ritual; karaoke song \"Tequila\"; awarded best sportsmanship in initiation run.</p>\n","related":[{"id":"concepts/chelympics","label":"Chelympics"},{"id":"summaries/2025-05-09-initiation-to-chelympics-1-beer-1-shot-per-person","label":"Chelympics — Initiation Rules and Scoring"},{"id":"entities/yahir-family","label":"Yahir's Family"}]}
